teamPageText:
Google is known all around the world. Everyone is 'googling', checking on 'maps' and communicating in 'gmail'. For simple users, they are services that just works, but not for us. Developers see much more: APIs, scalability issues, complex technology stacks. And that is what Google I/O (Extended) is about.

Google I/O 2017 Extended IUT is a conference of geek comunity to share their passion in tech, new experiments and network with local developer community.

Our goal is to organize space to connect the best industry experts with University students and beginners to boost development of IT.
